import React from 'react'

export default function PauseButton(props) {
  return (
    <button {...props}>
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        className="h-6 w-6"
        fill="none"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        stroke="currentColor"
        strokeWidth={2}
      >
        <path
          strokeLinecap="round"
          strokeLinejoin="round"
          d="M10 9v6m4-6v6m7-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
        />
      </svg>
    </button>
  );
}
